<div class="p text-right font-secondary"><a href="table/t3-amia2005_0106/" class="usa-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open in a new tab</a></div></section></section><section id="sec12"><h3 class="pmc_sec_title">4.2 Results of the intrinsic evaluation</h3>
<p>Two raters (HC, GM) had an overall agreement of 83.3% and a kappa
of 0.611. (<a href="#t4-amia2005_0106" class="usa-link">Table 4</a>) If the associations scored 1 or 2 were considered true associations and
those scored 3 were false associations, the kappa increased to 0.764.</p>
