<div class="p text-right font-secondary"><a href="table/t4-amia2005_0106/" class="usa-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open in a new tab</a></div></section><p>For KB-χ<sup>2</sup>, 72.2% of the associations were considered to be direct associations, 21.9% to
be indirection associations, and 6% to
be false associations. For KB-PCI, 52% were judged to be direct
associations, 24.8% to be indirect associations, and 23.2% to
be false associations. (<a href="#t5-amia2005_0106" class="usa-link">Table 5</a>)</p>
